    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tools_ja",
      "x": 225,
      "y": 298,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Tools:\n• fetch_jobs — scrape Indeed / LinkedIn\n• select_jobs_by_group — filter by title groups\n• save_skills_for_insertion — store approved skills\n• delete_market_skills — remove from Neo4j\n• show_current_state — diagnostic dump\n\nHandoffs → Skill Extractor, Concept Linker",
