      "text": "Tools:\n• extract_skills_llm\n  Parallel batch extraction (ThreadPool)\n  Batches ×5 jobs, deduplicates results\n  Returns: name, category, frequency, %\n\nHandoffs → Curriculum Mapper, Job Analyst",
